{"tid":1524291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全部遠離地鐵站先!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:58:48.000Z","uid":62011,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc73edeb9f4d74e543c04e680d517158a2e638f","tid":1524291,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:57:33.000Z","msg":"今晚警方行動根本是無差別大搜捕，每個警區派多隊防暴守住港鐵站出口，必要時衝入車廂拉人，也巡視歸家途人是否似示威者。<br />\n<br />\n就算唔係示威者，只要警隊人數夠多之下搜查港鐵乘客背囊等等，有任何疑似示威物品都會立即被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n根本係亂黎，未歸家既大家報個平安比屋企先，然後盡量去搵酒店訓一晚，或者附近有無朋友借宿。"},{"pid":"803538424b9a117a1b21384a60c16d5d202a4213","tid":1524291,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:58:45.000Z","msg":"香港地鐵<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/69442564_10158010058727448_3356278038563127296_n.png.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQnpVSNWJ-mA3qYoC28-lnpoLuBnaHEVEEVabpOvS2FPMXk7vZl15hqRGJeGN9SmDMs&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=9f70e814864162f7d2b3ee2d68b60696&amp;oe=5E09B98A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F69442564_10158010058727448_3356278038563127296_n.png.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQnpVSNWJ-mA3qYoC28-lnpoLuBnaHEVEEVabpOvS2FPMXk7vZl15hqRGJeGN9SmDMs%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D9f70e814864162f7d2b3ee2d68b60696%26oe%3D5E09B98A&h=761d5db4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f20b7180698318116fc91cbadb2f93394ce1eca","tid":1524291,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:58:48.000Z","msg":"［文宣超新星爆炸］ 魔警阻止人道救援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMjHJNz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMjHJNz.jpg&h=3027d600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.